reviewText:
I can't BELIEVE IT,

this He-man UMD is the strangest of all time,

for me it is the best collection I've ever heared, for He-man's fans its the best 5 episodes of He-man & The Masters of the Universe part 2, you must have it, it contains:

-Origin of the Sorceress

-The Problem with Power

-To Save Skeletor

-Teela's Triumph

-Into the Abyss

I am very happy to have it on PSP UMD

I can't wait any longer YEEEESSSS
